    "We also specified in the prompt that the story should be around 1, 000 words long.",
    "For each of the 108 participants, 5 stories were generated by randomly selecting 5 out of the 6 models, resulting in a total of 540 stories.",
    "Prompts were also randomly sampled from our pool to ensure balanced representation across Hofstede's cultural layers.Annotation Interface.",
    "We developed a custom span annotation interface building on Factgenie [41].",
    "This interface enabled participants to highlight spans in the story, tag the relevant category of misrepresentation, and add comments to support their annotations."
